Pure-Rust, CPU-hyper-optimized runner for the Baidu Unlimited-OCR model

Usage: focr <COMMAND>

Commands:
  ocr        Parse a document image into structured markdown (or `--json`)
  ocr-batch  OCR many images in ONE process — load the 6.2 GB weights + build the int8 decoder cache ONCE, then stream a result per image (the throughput path)
  convert    Offline weight transformation: safetensors → `.focrq` (plan §5)
  pull       Download the model weights (int8 `.focrq` + tokenizer) into the cache
  models     List the models this build can run (the "model zoo"): id, tasks, status
  robot      Agent-facing diagnostics and the machine contract
  runs       Query durable run history (fsqlite-backed store lands with plan §7.2)
  sync       Export/import the append-only run audit stream
  doctor     Idempotent self-check / repair
  help       Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version
